{
  "text": "The literature on socially differential effects of smoking interventions is sparse, especially when investigating interventions among adolescents [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] . We want to use the X:IT evaluation to examine the socially differential effects of our intervention: Does it have equal effects among school children from both high and low socioeconomic positions or does it widen the socioeconomic gap in smoking behavior?",
  "correct_citation": {
